### Compiling Collections

[Product Hunt also employs the recycling mechanic perfectly](#twitter): their “Collections” feature lets members create their own lists of products organized around a theme: this not only gives members a sense of ownership and engagement with the site, but it's also a great way to help resurface older content for new members. 

